snippet.title: Omni - Weapons Introduction First Look
snippet.description:
OMNI is a massively multiplayer online shooter slash loot game (MMOSSL). 

In Omni you can choose from many different types of weapons. Changing your gear changes your play style and abilities. You need to choose wisely, since some weapons are more effective than others against certain types of enemies. 

Omni Webpage: https://www.play-omni.com/
